{"parse":{"title":"Raw Glossy Mightfish","pageid":59913,"wikitext":{"*":"<onlyinclude>{{{{{tpl|tooltip}}}\n|mode={{{mode|}}}\n|arg={{{arg|}}}\n|icon=INV_Misc_MonsterHead_03\n|stack=20\n|name=Raw Glossy Mightfish\n|quality=common\n|level=35\n|cooldown=1 sec\n|effect=Use: Restores 810 health over 27 sec. Must remain seated while eating.\n|sell={{cost|||6}}\n|ilvl=45\n}}</onlyinclude>\n'''Raw Glossy Mightfish''' is a fish that can be cooked into [[Cooked Glossy Mightfish]], a food item that provides 10 [[stamina]] for 10 minutes.\n\n== Source ==\nRaw Glossy Mightfish can be caught in [[Azshara]], [[Badlands]], [[Feralas]], [[Stranglethorn Vale]], [[Tanaris]] and [[The Hinterlands]].\n\n== Raw Glossy Mightfish as an Ingredient ==\n\n=== Cooking ===\n*{{loot|common|Cooked Glossy Mightfish}}\n\n==External links==\n<!-- Read http://www.wowwiki.com/WoWWiki:External_links before posting your links here.\nLinks that do not conform to the rules will be DELETED.\nRepeat violations may result in a BAN.\nHave a nice day. :) -->\n{{elinks-item|13754}}\n{{Elink|link=http://www.elsanglin.com/fish/raw_glossy_mightfish.html |site=El's Extreme Anglin' |icon=elsanglin}}\n[[Category:World of Warcraft common fished items]]\n[[Category:World of Warcraft food items]]\n[[Category:World of Warcraft cooking ingredient items]]"}}}